OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable amounts of cloud but a
OL,6,Fgenerally dry, bright and rather warm
OL,7,Fday. Cloud increasing by late
OL,8,Fafternoon, perhaps bringing some light
OL,9,Frain into the west by early evening.
OL,10,FLocally breezy during the afternoon,
OL,11,Fotherwise winds fairly light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FTurning cloudy across all
OL,14,Fparts through the evening with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of mainly light rain
OL,16,Fspreading east overnight. Chance of
OL,17,Fsome heavier bursts of rain in the far
OL,18,Fwest after dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
