OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FCloudy with some intermittent
OL,6,Frain at first. Persistent rain with
OL,7,Fembedded heavier pulses, spreads east
OL,8,Fduring the morning and early
OL,9,Fafternoon, followed by brighter
OL,10,Fconditions and scattered, possibly
OL,11,Fthundery showers.
OL,12,
OL,13,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,14,FSunshine and showers Tuesday and
OL,15,FWednesday with a risk of hail and
OL,16,Fthunder. A fine start likely on
OL,17,FThursday, then rain arriving later.
OL,18,FBreezy at times and rather cool
OL,19,Foverall.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
